~~> Unlimited Mapper <~~
# Map by Plastik!!!

[Informations]
# 28 slot. (14 blue cars)(14 red cars)
# In this map you musst knife/crash the other people's cars.
# It's funny because you can control your own car (t=red/ct=blue)
and you are faster if you go,as normaly.The cars are BMWs ,because 
I think they looks great in this map.
# It's better to run this map on your server with "noblock".
# After 70 sec,the lasers in the middle will be deactivated and
you can get a hegrenade.
# I hope you like my map and the style!
# Please rate for it and perhaps visit us!
